    {
      "text": "Battle Formation was a strategy game for the PlayStation that used villains from the Ultraman, Gundam, and Kamen Rider franchises as playable characters. The player would use mobile suits, kaijin, and Kaiju from various entries of each franchise to conquer an island until they encountered the final boss simply known as Keeper.",
